Reasoning: The paper presents a formalisation of the core of the theory of CCS in the HOL theorem prover, which is a topic related to logic and automated reasoning (cs.LO) and programming languages (cs.PL). The focus of the paper is on the theory of unique solutions of contractions, which is a topic related to semantics (cs.LF) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper also discusses some refinements of the theory itself, which is a topic related to formal languages and automata (cs.FL).
